# Learning Quran and Dua by playing games

Enjoying and justifing the knowlege of Quran and Dua through playing games. Listen a audio sound from quran and user need to store Sura of 
the Ayah in a Bag to increase his/her score and for this he/she have three lives and three level. To get better score to collect sura more
into the Bag. Highest score will be store in the database server and local memory. In case of database failure, the games fatches data from
local directory. 
